<style>
:root{
  --ts-xl:2.2rem; --navy:#111111; --red:#0188CC; --ink:#111111; --muted:#666666;
  --gold-soft:rgba(1,136,204,.10); --gold-line:rgba(1,136,204,.24);
  --fh:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif; --fb:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:93%}
body{font-family:var(--fb);background:#fff;color:#333;line-height:1.6;}

.values-section{padding:96px 48px;background:#fff}
.sec-head{text-align:center;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto 56px}
.sec-label{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--fb);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:16px;}
.sec-label::before{content:"";width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--red);}
.sec-label::after{content:"";width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--red);}
.sec-h{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:var(--ts-xl);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:14px;font-weight:400;}
.sec-h em{font-style:italic;color:var(--red)}
.sec-sub{font-family:var(--fb);font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;}

.values-grid{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:22px;}
.value-card{text-align:center;padding:32px 22px}
.value-icon{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold-soft);border:1px solid var(--gold-line);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 18px;}
.value-icon svg{width:26px;height:26px;stroke:var(--navy);stroke-width:1.8;fill:none}
.value-card h4{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.22rem;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:400;}
.value-card p{font-family:var(--fb);font-size:.88rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;}

@media(max-width:880px){.values-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.values-section{padding:68px 22px}}
@media(max-width:480px){.values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>

<section class="values-section">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <span class="sec-label">What We Stand For</span>
    <h2 class="sec-h">Our <em>Core Values</em></h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">Four principles that guide every job that leaves our factory floor.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L3 7v6c0 5.5 3.8 10.7 9 12 5.2-1.3 9-6.5 9-12V7l-9-5z"/></svg></div>
      <h4>Built to Last</h4>
      <p>UL-listed components, commercial-grade materials, weather-rated finishes. A sign should outlast the lease.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L9 18l-5-5"/></svg></div>
      <h4>Honest Pricing</h4>
      <p>Transparent quotes, clear line items, no surprise add-ons. You see exactly what you pay for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></div>
      <h4>On Time, Every Time</h4>
      <p>If we commit to a date, we hit the date. Production schedules are built around your lease and grand opening.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg></div>
      <h4>People Over Process</h4>
      <p>Someone picks up the phone. A designer builds the mockup. A foreman runs your job from start to finish.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "NT About Values",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "NT About Values"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}